@s1!a4 "r13_seed_hexad_200"|"서술 요청 (hexad): rust/consciousness."|"rust/consciousness.hexa Cell division engine for consciousness specialization. Cells are small ConsciousMind instances that divide when tension exceeds a threshold, with each child specializing on different topics. API - `ConsciousMind(input_dim=64, hidden_dim=128, output_dim=64)` -- Self-contained PureField + GRU cell - `MitosisEngine(input_dim, hidden_dim, output_dim, initial_cells=2, max_cells=64)` -- Multi-cell consciousness manager - `.process(x) -> dict` -- run input through all cells, return tensions/outputs - `._create_cell(parent)` -- create new cell from parent - `."|"docs/modules/mitosis.md"|"hexad"|1.0|~|1|200|4096|"BT-1427"|"BT-1423"|[]|"multimodal_safety"|false|true|0.9004|21.6099|true|"corpus_generator_v2.hexa"
