esc 0.95 vs code 0.99) | | V17 | TEMPORAL_LZ | genuine | 측정 OK | NATURAL | PASS | LZ=0.996, periodic kill-switch 없음 | | V18 | INFO_INTEGRATION | scale | 측정 OK | NATURAL | PASS | Phi@16 > Phi@4 (1.11 vs 0."|"docs/12_conditions_audit_20260419.md"|"law"|1.0|~|1|200|4096|"BT-1422"|"BT-1426"|["IIT"]|"adversarial_robustness"|false|true|false|"corpus_generator_v2.hexa"
