@s2!a4 "r13_seed_persona_1347"|"Layer 2: Direction reversal detection ├─ Dot product sign between consecutive pairs ├─ High flip rate = contradictory signals └─ flip_rate × 1."|"Layer 2: Direction reversal detection ├─ Dot product sign between consecutive pairs ├─ High flip rate = contradictory signals └─ flip_rate × 1.5 penalty Layer 3: Pairwise similarity variance ├─ All-pairs cosine similarity ├─ True signals: low variance └─ var > 0.05 starts penalizing Dedekind ratio: ψ(ψ(6))/ψ(6) = σ(6)/6 = 2 → ratio ≈ 2 = \"perfect transmission\" (lossless) **Evolution:** True/False 44% (1-channel) → 92."|"docs/modules/tension_link.md"|"persona"|1.0|~|1|200|4096|"BT-1425"|"BT-1424"|[]|""|false|true|false|"corpus_generator_v2.hexa"
